<item>
            <title>[FLINK-6659] RocksDBMergeIteratorTest, SavepointITCase leave temporary directories behind</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6659</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;RocksDBMergeIteratorTest&lt;/tt&gt; uses a newly created temporary directory (via &lt;tt&gt;CommonTestUtils.createTempDirectory()&lt;/tt&gt;) for its RocksDB instance but does not delete is when finished. We should better replace this pattern with a proper &lt;tt&gt;@Rule&lt;/tt&gt;-based approach&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13073889">FLINK-6659</key>
            <summary>RocksDBMergeIteratorTest, SavepointITCase leave temporary directories behind</summary>
